OL,3,CGovernment set to announce details of
OL,4,Cpackage to help Tata Steel plant
OL,6,FThe Government is expected to announce
OL,7,Fdetails of a multimillion-pound
OL,8,Fpackage to help the transition to a
OL,9,Fgreener way of producing steel at
OL,10,FTata's Port Talbot site.
OL,12,FTata Steel is planning to change the
OL,13,Fway it produces steel at its site in
OL,14,FPort Talbot in South Wales, with the
OL,15,Floss of up to 2,800 jobs.
