OL,3,CGovernment set to announce details of
OL,4,Cpackage to help Tata Steel plant
OL,6,FThe company will close the remaining
OL,7,Fblast furnace at Port Talbot by the
OL,8,Fend of the month in readiness for
OL,9,Fswitching production with a new
OL,10,Felectric arc furnace which needs fewer
OL,11,Fworkers.
OL,13,FThe Business Secretary, Jonathan
OL,14,FReynolds, is expected to outline on
OL,15,FWednesday details of a deal to help
OL,16,Fwith the transition.
