OL,3,CGovernment set to announce details of
OL,4,Cpackage to help Tata Steel plant
OL,6,FThe previous Conservative government
OL,7,Fhad agreed to give Tata Steel #500
OL,8,Fmillion towards the #1.25 billion
OL,9,Felectric furnace, which will melt
OL,10,Fscrap steel.
OL,12,FUnions have been campaigning to save
OL,13,Fjobs at Port Talbot, warning that the
OL,14,Flosses would have a huge impact on the
OL,15,Flocal economy.
